Realtime, WebGl based, audioreactive, reflective, animated, hyperpainting, dont forget to allow microphone input access in your browser
The hdr sky cube box is generated from a spheric panorama taken in the University's of Art and Design Offenbach am Main backyard.

Live demo: https://aznbai.github.io/hyperpainting-audioreactive-webgl
More info: http://hyperpainting.net
